506
00:27:07,086 --> 00:27:08,670
Am I right so far?

507
00:27:08,671 --> 00:27:10,880
- Yes, you are.
- You bet he is.

508
00:27:10,881 --> 00:27:14,134
He talked with his friends for about
an hour, leaving them at 9:45.

509
00:27:14,135 --> 00:27:17,178
During this time,
they saw the switch knife.

510
00:27:17,179 --> 00:27:19,055
Four.

511
00:27:19,056 --> 00:27:21,558
They identified the death
weapon in court...

512
00:27:21,559 --> 00:27:24,144
as that very same knife.

513
00:27:24,145 --> 00:27:27,022
Five. He arrived
home at about 10:00.

514
00:27:27,023 --> 00:27:29,441
Now this is where the stories
offered by the State and the boy...

