537
00:28:30,294 --> 00:28:32,587
and that somebody else stabbed
his father with a similar knife.

538
00:28:32,588 --> 00:28:33,880
It's just possible.

539
00:28:33,881 --> 00:28:35,565
Take a look at this knife.

540
00:28:37,385 --> 00:28:39,677
It's a very unusual knife.

541
00:28:39,678 --> 00:28:41,304
I've never seen one like it.

542
00:28:41,305 --> 00:28:44,182
