544
00:28:47,228 --> 00:28:49,646
I'm just saying a
coincidence is possible.

545
00:28:49,647 --> 00:28:51,247
And I say it's not possible.

546
00:28:57,780 --> 00:28:59,572
Where did that come from?

547
00:28:59,573 --> 00:29:01,032
