561
00:29:33,858 --> 00:29:35,733
with exactly the
same kind of knife?

562
00:29:35,734 --> 00:29:37,068
The odds are a million-to-one.

563
00:29:37,069 --> 00:29:39,879
- It's possible.
- But not very probable.

564
00:29:40,990 --> 00:29:43,074
Okay, fellas, let's take our seats.

565
00:29:43,075 --> 00:29:45,236
There's no point in standing
around all over the place.

566
00:29:46,745 --> 00:29:50,248
You know, it's interesting that he'd find a
knife exactly like the one the boy bought.

567
00:29:50,249 --> 00:29:53,084
What's interesting about it?
Interesting.

568
00:29:53,085 --> 00:29:55,044
Well, I don't know. I just
thought it was interesting.

569
00:29:55,045 --> 00:29:56,921
There are still 11 of us
here who think he's guilty.

570
00:29:56,922 --> 00:29:59,299
Right. What do you think
