574
00:30:08,267 --> 00:30:10,226
That's probably right.

575
00:30:10,227 --> 00:30:13,521
So what are you gonna do?
You know, we could be here all night.

576
00:30:13,522 --> 00:30:16,858
It's only one night.
A boy may die.

577
00:30:16,859 --> 00:30:19,486
Well, why don't we just
set up house here, huh?

578
00:30:19,487 --> 00:30:22,030
Someone send for Potsy the
