584
00:30:38,797 --> 00:30:41,591
I got three garages of mine goin'
to pot while you're talking.

585
00:30:41,592 --> 00:30:43,343
So let's get done
and get outta here.

586
00:30:43,344 --> 00:30:46,846
The knife was very important to the
district attorney. He spent a whole day...

587
00:30:46,847 --> 00:30:49,390
He's a 15th assistant or something.
What does he know about it?

588
00:30:49,391 --> 00:30:50,934
Hey, let's hold it down.

589
00:30:50,935 --> 00:30:53,369
These side arguments
are only slowing us up.

590
00:30:56,148 --> 00:30:57,607
Well, what about it?

591
00:30:57,608 --> 00:30:59,208
You're the only one.

592
00:31:07,034 --> 00:31:09,177
I have a proposition
to make to all of you.

593
00:31:10,162 --> 00:31:12,013
I'm gonna call for another vote.

594
00:31:13,374 --> 00:31:18,670
I want you 11 men to vote
by secret written ballot.

595
00:31:18,671 --> 00:31:20,797
I'll abstain.

596
00:31:20,798 --> 00:31:23,675
If there are 11 votes for guilty,
I won't stand alone.

597
00:31:23,676 --> 00:31:27,570
We'll take in a guilty verdict
to the judge right now.

598
00:31:28,931 --> 00:31:32,742
But if anyone votes not guilty,
we stay here and talk it out.

599
00:31:35,980 --> 00:31:38,982
Well, that's it. If you
want to try it, I'm ready.

600
00:31:38,983 --> 00:31:40,525
All right.
Let's do it the hard way.

601
00:31:40,526 --> 00:31:42,527
Okay, that sounds fair.
Everyone agreed?

